Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.90,0:25:36.35,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,Falling perfect lighten the focal
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.90,0:25:36.59,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,Following the brake light of the front car.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.59,0:25:42.20,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,Kurai michi no saki ni bonyari nijimu akari{A shimmering light up ahead in the dark street.}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.65,0:25:42.54,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,暗い道の先にぼんやりにじむ明かり
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.78,0:25:46.43,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,It's the silence like a silent film.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.99,0:25:46.34,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,If the tires strike a silent wind
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.79,0:25:50.79,Karaoke Translation op,...CAST3:...,0,0,0,,{\3c&H141416&\pos(732,413)}A\NCentral Anime\NProduction\N\NTranslation:\NHiro-kun\N\NTiming:\NTodd Perkins\N\NEditing:\NBarbara\NTodd Perkins\NBrain\NDave\NMouse
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.43,0:25:52.40,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,Tayori ni naru mono wa sore shika mienakatta{The light was all I could depend on.}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.52,0:25:52.38,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,頼りになるものはそれしか見えなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.15,0:25:58.23,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,Kono namiki michi wo nukete ikeba kitto{I felt like I could catch it...}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.18,0:25:58.12,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,この並木道を抜けていけばきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.23,0:26:01.76,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,Tsukameru youna ki ga shita{...if I passed through this tree-lined street.}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.30,0:26:01.70,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,つかめるような気がした
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.76,0:26:05.40,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,Get up! I just can't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.83,0:26:05.38,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,Give up! I just can't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.40,0:26:11.85,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,Sokoniwa mada sagashimono wa nani mo nakute{I couldn't find what I'd been looking for.}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.51,0:26:11.92,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,外にはまだ捜し物は何もなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.85,0:26:15.34,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,Yeah, it starts at this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.04,0:26:15.32,尾曲-日-ja,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It stops at this moment
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.34,0:26:19.01,Karaoke Translation op,..SONG...,0,0,0,,Kono basho kara{At this place.}
